\c 1
\s Okhokho bakaJesu
\p
\v 1 Ugwalo lokuzalwa kukaJesu Kristu\x + Luka 3.23-38.\x*, iNdodana kaDavida\x + Hlab. 132.11. Isa. 11.1. Jer. 23.5. Mat. 22.42. Luka 1.32,69. Joha. 7.42. Seb. 2.30; 13.23. Roma 1.3. 2 Tim. 2.8. Mat. 9.27.\x*, indodana kaAbrahama\x + Gen. 12.3; 22.18. Gal. 3.16.\x*.
\v 2 UAbrahama wazala\x + Luka 3.34-32.\x* uIsaka\x + Gen. 21.2,3.\x*; uIsaka wasezala uJakobe\x + Gen. 25.26.\x*; uJakobe wasezala uJuda labafowabo\x + Gen. 29.35.\x*;
\v 3 uJuda wasezala uFaresi loZara kuTamari\x + Gen. 38.27-30.\x*; uFaresi wasezala uEsiromu\x + Ruthe 4.18-22. 1 Lan. 2.4-12.\x*; uEsiromu wasezala uAramu;
\v 4 uAramu wasezala uAminadaba; uAminadaba wasezala uNashoni; uNashoni wasezala uSalimoni;
\v 5 uSalimoni wasezala uBowosi kuRahabi\x + Josh. 6.25.\x*; uBowosi wasezala uObedi kuRuthe; uObedi wasezala uJese;
\v 6 uJese wasezala uDavida inkosi\x + 1 Sam. 16.1; 17.12.\x*; uDavida inkosi wasezala uSolomoni ko\add wayengum\add*kaUriya\x + 2 Sam. 12.24.\x*;
\v 7 uSolomoni wasezala uRehobhowamu; uRehobhowamu wasezala uAbhiya; uAbhiya wasezala uAsa;
\v 8 uAsa wasezala uJehoshafathi; uJehoshafathi wasezala uJoramu; uJoramu wasezala uOziya;
\v 9 uOziya wasezala uJothamu; uJothamu wasezala uAhazi; uAhazi wasezala uHezekhiya\x + 1 Lan. 3.10-14.\x*;
\v 10 uHezekhiya wasezala uManase\x + 2 Kho. 20.21.\x*; uManase wasezala uAmoni; uAmoni wasezala uJosiya;
\v 11 uJosiya wasezala uJekoniya labafowabo\x + 1 Lan. 3.15,16.\x* esikhathini sokuthunjelwa eBhabhiloni\x + 2 Kho. 24.14,15,16; 25.11. Jer. 27.20. Dan. 1.2.\x*.
\v 12 Kwathi emva kokuthunjelwa eBhabhiloni uJekoniya\x + 1 Lan. 3.17-19.\x* wazala uSalatiyeli\x + Ezra 3.2.\x*; uSalatiyeli wasezala uZerubhabheli\x + Ezra 3.2.\x*\x + 1 Lan. 3.19.\x*;
\v 13 uZerubhabheli wasezala uAbiyudi; uAbiyudi wasezala uEliyakhimi; uEliyakhimi wasezala uAzori;
\v 14 uAzori wasezala uZadoki; uZadoki wasezala uAkimi; uAkimi wasezala uEliyudi;
\v 15 uEliyudi wasezala uEleyazare; uEleyazare wasezala uMathani; uMathani wasezala uJakobe;
\v 16 uJakobe wasezala uJosefa indoda kaMariya, okwazalwa kuye uJesu othiwa nguKristu.
\p
\v 17 Ngakho izizukulwana zonke ezisukela kuAbrahama zisiya kuDavida ziyizizukulwana ezilitshumi lane; lezisukela kuDavida ziye ekuthunjelweni eBhabhiloni ziyizizukulwana ezilitshumi lane; lezisukela ekuthunjelweni eBhabhiloni ziye kuKristu ziyizizukulwana ezilitshumi lane.
\s Ukuzalwa kukaJesu
\p
\v 18 Ngakho ukuzalwa kukaJesu Kristu kwaba nje\x + Luka 1.27.\x*. Ngoba unina uMariya esegane uJosefa, bengakahlangani wabonakala eselesisu ngoMoya oNgcwele\x + Luka 1.35.\x*.
\v 19 Kodwa uJosefa indoda yakhe engolungileyo\x + Hlab. 112.4.\x*, njalo engathandi ukumthela ihlazo, wayefuna ukumala ensitha\x + Dute. 22.13-21; 24.1.\x*.
\v 20 Kwathi esanakana lezizinto, khangela, ingilosi yeNkosi yabonakala kuye ephutsheni\x + 2.12.\x*, esithi: Josefa, ndodana kaDavida, ungesabi ukumthatha uMariya umkakho; ngoba lokho akukhulelweyo\f + \fk akukhulelweyo: \fl Gr. \fq wazala\f* kungoMoya oNgcwele;
\v 21 njalo uzazala indodana\x + Luka 1.31.\x*, ubize ibizo layo \add uthi\add* nguJesu\f + u\fk Jesu: \ft okutsho, \fq uMsindisi, \ft Heb.\f*; ngoba yena uzasindisa abantu bakhe\x + Seb. 4.12; 13.23.\x* ezonweni zabo\x + Seb. 5.31; 13.38.\x*.
\v 22 Konke lokhu-ke kwenzeka ukuze kugcwaliseke okwakhulunywa yiNkosi ngomprofethi ukuthi:
\v 23 Khangela, intombi izathatha isisu ibelethe indodana\x + Isa. 7.14.\x*, njalo bazabiza\f + \fk bazabiza: \ft kumbe, \fq ibizo lakhe lizathiwa\f* ibizo layo \add ngokuthi\add* nguEmanuweli, okuyikuthi ngokuphendulelwa, uNkulunkulu ulathi.
\v 24 Kwathi uJosefa esephapheme ebuthongweni wenza njengalokho ingilosi yeNkosi imlayile, wasethatha umkakhe;
\v 25 kodwa kazange amazi waze\x + Gen. 28.15. 1 Sam. 15.35. 2 Sam. 6.23. 1 Lan. 28.20. Isa. 22.14.\x* wabeletha indodana yakhe eyingqabutho\x + Eks. 13.2. Luka 2.7.\x*; wasebiza ibizo layo \add wathi\add* nguJesu\x + Gen. 38.4,5. 1 Lan. 7.16. Luka 1.31; 2.21.\x*.